Taron Trump na zaben West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai kaddamar da yakin neman zabensa a Wheeling, West Virginia, a daren yau.
Wannan shi ne taron farko na yakin neman zaben Trump na mako guda biyar, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da aka yi wa kuri'ar amincewa har sai da Trump ya zaɓi wanda zai nada a matsayin babban kotun, yana ƙoƙarin ƙara goyon baya ga zaɓen zagaye na gaba, saboda 'yan Republican suna barazanar rasa iko a cikin majalisa bayan zaben a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron yakin neman zaben Trump a West Virginia a daren yau, kuma ta yaya za a kalli wannan a Intanet?
A ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018, da yamma, a Wheeling, West Virginia, za a yi taron yakin neman zaben Trump a karfe 7:00 na yammacin gabas.
Za a iya kallon taron yakin neman zaben Trump a West Virginia a kan layi ta hanyar tashar YouTube.
A lokacin da ake zargin cewa an yi lalata da shi, an dakatar da zaben Majalisar Dattawa na mako guda don a amince da shi har sai da FBI ta yi bincike.
Amma babban manufar wannan jerin zaɓen shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar babban zaɓe a watan Nuwamba su sami sabon iko.
Shugaba Trump ya ce, shirin da za a yi a mako mai zuwa zai yi wa masu aikin sa kai da magoya bayansa aiki yayin da 'yan Republican ke ƙoƙarin kare da kuma faɗaɗa rinjayen su a Majalisar Dattawa da Majalisar Dattijai, in ji Reuters.
"Saki na majalisar wakilai yana da mahimmanci ga tsarin shugaban kasa, saboda haka Trump zai yi tafiya cikin sauri don shiga cikin yawancin jihohi a lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun yakin Trump ga Reuters, wanda bai so ya ambaci sunansa ba.
An shirya taron da za a yi a filin wasa na Wesbanco a Wheeling a daren yau da dare, kuma zai iya jawo masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma a cikin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, West Virginia Metro News ta ruwaito.
Wannan ne karo na biyu da Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia a cikin wata guda da ya gabata, a jihar da ya samu fiye da kashi 40 cikin 100 na kuri'un da aka kada a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar Sanata na Jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ke jagorantar 'yan takarar da ke neman neman tallafi.
"Ba abin da ya dace da Morrisy ba ne cewa shugaban ya zo ya ƙarfafa sakamakonsa", in ji masanin siyasa na Jami'ar West Virginia, Simon Haeder, a cewar Reuters.
