Turai za ta iya samun ci gaba mai kyau a ranar ƙarshe ta gasar Ryder Cup, ta ci gaba da yin nasara a kan Amurka 106 a wasan hudu da biyu na Asabar.
Babban ma'aurata Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci Tiger Woods da ke fama da matsaloli da nasara biyu don haɓaka ƙimar su zuwa maki huɗu a Le Golf National.
Thomas Bjorne na Turai, wanda ya ci gaba da tsaron da aka yi a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka shige, ya ci nasara a wasan da ya yi a Amirka a wasan da ya yi a wasan da ya yi, kuma ya ci wasan da 3-1.
Ƙasar Amirka ta yi nasara a wasan biyu, amma ba ta iya biyan bukatarsu ba.
Jim Fury na bukatar maki takwas don ci gaba da tseren a wasanni 12 na yau da kullum.
