Farfesa Jay Berzofsky daga Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon daji ta Amirka a Bethesda, Maryland, ya bayyana cewa: "Bincikenmu ya nuna cewa muna da alurar riga kafi mai ban sha'awa.
Farfesa Berzofsky ya bayyana cewa, HER2  yana sa ciwon daji ya ƙaru a wasu nau'o'in daji, ciki har da na nono, na kwai, na huhu, da na colorectal.
An yi amfani da irin wannan tsarin wajen karbar kwayoyin rigakafi daga marasa lafiya kuma a koya musu su yi amfani da kwayoyin cutar kansa wajen magance wasu nau'ikan cututtukan leukemia.
