Wani ɗan fim mai suna Johnny English Strikes Again - wani ɗan leƙen asiri na Rowan Atkinson
A yau, ana yin amfani da sabon fim din Birtaniya don neman ma'anar Brexit, kuma wannan ya zama abin da ya dace sosai ga jerin shirye-shiryen wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English - wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya biyo baya a 2011 tare da sake farfadowa Johnny English Reborn.
Shin muna da wata ha'inci ta yin ba'a game da yadda muka kasance wauta game da sabon damar fitar da kayayyaki a kasar?
Ko ta yaya, Johnny English, wanda ba shi da basira kuma yana da idanu masu nauyi, ya sake samun izini ya sake yin abubuwa a hanyarsa ta banƙyama - kuma wannan babban wasan kwaikwayo na ban dariya na musamman don fina-finai na ba Turanci ba.
Hakika, wannan wani jami'in asiri ne wanda duk da cewa yana da irin wannan sha'awar da ya yi na yin amfani da kayan ado na zamani, yana kama da Clouseau, Mr Bean, da kuma wani ɗan wasan kwaikwayo wanda ya sa murya ga alamar Chariots of Fire a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta London 2012.
Har ila yau, an kafa shi ne bisa wani matafiyi da kuma wani mutum mai ban mamaki na duniya Atkinson, wanda aka yi wa rawa a cikin wani tallan talabijin na Barclayscard da aka manta da shi, wanda ya bar komai a baya.
A cikin fim ɗin nan na ƙarshe na JE, akwai lokatai ɗaya ko biyu masu ban sha'awa.
Ina son yadda Johnny English ya zo kusa da jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu yana ɗauke da rigar ƙarni na dā kuma a lokacin da ya yi amfani da fuka-fukan jirgin sama, sai ya yi ta yin tuntuɓe.
An nuna baiwar Atkins don yin wasan kwaikwayo na zahiri, amma ban dariya ya zama baƙon abu kuma yana da ban mamaki, musamman idan fina-finai masu zaman kansu kamar 007 da Mission Impossible suna ba da wasan kwaikwayo da kansu.
Wannan ba'a na yara ne kawai, ba manya ba, kuma a ganina, ba a san Johnny English ba da yawon shakatawa da kuma hankali kamar Atkins' dark films a Beanin.
A yau, a kullum, ana iya ɗauka cewa ƙasar Birtaniya tana cikin matsala.
Wani dan gwanin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin hanyar yanar gizo ta 'yan leken asiri na Burtaniya, yana bayyana ainihin dukkan jami'an 'yan sanda na Birtaniya, yana sa babban takaici ga wani jami'in gida - abin takaici, karamin rawar Kevin Eldon.
