Kuma wannan yana nufin Johnny English, wanda yanzu yake aiki a matsayin malamin makaranta a wani babban jami'a, yana koyar da shi a asirce yadda ake zama jami'in asiri: Ga wasu wurare masu kyau da English ke ba da makarantar leken asiri na Rock.
