Saboda haka, Batman da Robin, da kuma wuraren da ake zargi da sirrinsa, sun sake yin aiki, suna haɗuwa da kyakkyawan matar Ophelia Bulletova, wadda Olga Kurolenko ta kasance.
A lokaci guda, Firayim Minista ya shiga hannun wani mai fasaha mai ƙwarewa wanda ya ce zai iya magance duk matsalolin kwamfuta na Burtaniya: Jason Volta, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
English da Bough sun fara da irin wannan mafarkin da suka yi: suna ɓoye kansu a matsayin masu gabatar da rahoto, suna ƙone gidan cin abinci na Faransa; suna haifar da rikici, suna ɓoye a kan jirgin jirgin jirgin ruwa mai ban sha'awa na Volta; kuma English yana kunna ainihin tsari yayin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da babban kayan aikin gaskiya na gaskiya don gano abin da ke cikin gidan Volta.
