Masu bincike sun yi gargadin cewa 'yan Republican za su yi watsi da mata kafin zaben ta'addanci da aka yi a Kavanaugh
A lokacin da 'yan Republican da dama ke jiran kuma suke kare dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ake zargi da wasu hare-haren jima'i, masu bincike sun yi gargadin cewa za su ga tashin hankali a lokacin zaben da ke tafe, musamman daga mata.
A halin da ake ciki, an yi ta yin magana game da batun, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun nuna cewa suna son su ci gaba da yin zabe.
"Ba za a iya karɓar waɗannan abubuwa ba", in ji Grant Reeher, wani farfesa a makarantar siyasa ta Maxwell a Jami'ar Syracuse a wani labarin da ya wallafa a ranar Asabar ga The Hill.
Shugaban ya yi zargin cewa, ƙoƙarin da Sanata Jeff Flake (R.A. Arizona) ya yi na ƙarshe game da binciken FBI ya isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a da suka yi fushi.
'Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru a jiya ba, ba za su manta da shi ba gobe ko a watan Nuwamba,' in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara ga ƙungiyar masu ci gaba da motsi ta MoveOn kuma mai ba da shawara ga gwamnati a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jaridar Washington DC.
A ranar Jumma'a da safe, masu zanga-zangar sun sake cewa "November na zuwa!" a wani zanga-zanga a cikin gidan majalisar dattawa, saboda 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitocin alƙalai sun yanke shawarar ci gaba da takarar Kavanaugh, duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, Mic ya sanar.
Democratic India da kuma fitar da kayayyaki na cikin gida sun fara fita daga jadawalin, in ji mai bincike kan siyasa Stu Rothenberg, mai ba da shawara ba.
Mutane suna cewa yana da tsayi, gaskiya ne.
Amma hakan na iya zama mafi girma, musamman a tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a a birane masu nisa da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a masu shekaru 1829 waɗanda ba sa son shugaban kasa kuma galibi ba sa jefa kuri'a.
Kafin Ford ya ba da shaida a fili, wanda ya bayyana zarginsa na yin lalata da dan takarar kotun tarayya, masana sun yi hasashen cewa za a yi farmaki idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da amincewa da hakan.
"Wannan ya zama abin ban haushi ga jam'iyyar GOP", in ji tsohon shugaban kwamitin jam'iyyar Republican Michael Steele a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
Wannan ba wai kawai game da zaɓe na kwamitin ba ne, ko kuma ko za a naɗa Kavanaugh, amma kuma game da yadda 'yan Republican suka bi da shi da kuma yadda suka bi da shi, shugaban Priorities USA Guy Cecil ya ba da labarin.
Duk da haka, Amirkawa sun nuna cewa sun rabu da juna, waɗanda suka gaskata da shaida a Ford da kuma waɗanda suka amince da Kavanaugh, amma sun fi son na farko.
Wani sabon bincike na YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun amince da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce sun amince da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce suna ganin Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da ya ba da shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari ne kawai suka yi hakan game da Ford.
Flake ya sa FBI na binciken zargin Ford da kuma akalla wani zargin Deborah Ramirez, jaridar The Guardian ta ruwaito.
A makon da ya gabata, Ford ya shaida a gaban Kwamitin Alƙalawa na Majalisar Dattawa cewa Kavanaugh ya kai masa hari sa'ad da yake ɗan shekara 17.
Ramirez ya ce wani ɗan takarar kotun tarayya ya nuna mata jima'i a lokacin da suke halartar wani biki a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin kaddamar da wani sabon intanet wanda zai hada Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ta duniya, ya kaddamar da wani kamfani wanda ke neman ya yi gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Aikin da aka yi na ƙarshe a cikin wannan al'adar fasaha shi ne Inrupt, wani kamfani da ke gina dandamali na Berners-Lee na tushen tushen tushen Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma ga wane mutane za a ba su damar samun damar yin amfani da su.
A wata hira da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi ta ba'a cewa Inrupt na da burin "mulkin duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi haka yanzu", in ji shi game da sabon kamfani.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Wannan app yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar ɗakunan ajiya na kan layi na kansu, ko POD.
Wannan zai iya ƙunshi jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyuka, kalandar, kundin kiɗa da sauran kayan aiki na mutum da na iya aiki.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack, da Spotify, duk suna samuwa a cikin mai bincike guda kuma a lokaci guda.
Abin da ya sa wannan rukunin yanar gizon kansa ya zama na musamman shi ne cewa mai amfani zai iya zaɓar wanda zai iya samun damar wannan bayanin.
Kamfanin yana kiran wannan don ba da izini ta hanyar bayanai.
A cewar shugaban kamfanin John Bruce, manufar Inrupt ita ce ta samar da tushen, tsari da kuma ƙwarewar da ta dace don taimakawa wajen samar da Solid ga kowa.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce Lee, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka da aka yi wa aiki don aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen shirye-shirye.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu fasahar kere-kere a faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen su na rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba za su tattauna da Facebook da Google ba ko za su yi cikakken canji idan an tallafa wa tsarin kasuwancin su gaba ɗaya.
Ba za mu nemi izinin su ba.
A wani sakon da ya wallafa a shafinsa na Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya ce, Inrupt na da burin samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu don taimakawa kare mutuncin da kuma ingancin sabon intanet da aka kirkira bisa Solid.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canja hanyar yin amfani da Intanet sa'ad da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance babbar murya a tattaunawar rashin son kai na cibiyar sadarwa.
Ko da bayan Inrupt ya fara aiki, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa mai kafa da kuma darektan World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation, da Open Data Institute.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da zamanin da za a yi amfani da intanet", in ji Berners-Lee.
