Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a sakamakon girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da ya afku a birnin Palut a ranar Juma'a, a ƙasar Indonesia, jami'ai sun ce, kuma sun ce adadin mutanen da suka mutu yana ci gaba da ƙaruwa.
Tun da aka hana sadarwa, ba a samu wani bayani daga rundunar Donggala da ke arewacin Palau, wadda ke kusa da wurin da girgizar ƙasa ta yi ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta yi.
An yi wa'azi a wurin fiye da mutane 16,000 bayan da aka yi wannan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu ita ce babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, a bakin tekun Sulawesi a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, kuma a shekara ta 2017, yawan mutanen wurin ya kai 379,800.
A lokacin da gari ya cika shekara 40, girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka addabe shi.
Ƙungiyar Donggala Regency wani yanki ne da ke da nisan mil 300 a arewacin Sulawesi.
A shekara ta 2017, an kiyasta yawan mutanen da ke cikin birnin Regens, wanda shi ne yankin da ke ƙarƙashin lardin.
Kasuwancin kifi da kuma noma sune manyan ayyukan tattalin arziki na lardin Tsakiya, musamman a yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Ana kuma yin amfani da nickel a lardin, wanda ya fi yawa a Morowali, a bakin tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'o'i ta Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami ya auku a Palau da Donggalau sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 a birnin Donggala, kuma ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje.
A shekara ta 1996, tsunami ya afku a yammacin birnin Donggala, ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yanayin da ke cikin tekun Pacific mai zafi kuma tana fuskantar girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu daga cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami mafi girma da aka yi a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da ta auku a yammacin yankin Aceh a arewacin Sumatra, Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ya auko wa ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabi a Aceh.
2005: A watan Maris da kuma farkon watan Afrilu, manyan girgizar ƙasa da yawa sun afku a yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane da yawa sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, wanda ke kusa da tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa tsibirin Java, wanda shi ne tsibirin da aka fi yawan zama a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta jawo tsunami da ya yi ta addabar tekun kudu da ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
A shekara ta 2009, girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afku a wani yanki kusa da Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afka wa tsibirin Mentawai na Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami mai tsayi har mita 10, wanda ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai zurfi ta afkawa birnin Asey a cikin yankin Pidie Jaya, ta jawo tsoro da kuma bala'i, ta tunasar da mutane game da mummunan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004.
Ba a yi tsunami a wannan lokacin ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 ne suka mutu a gine-ginen da suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mafi girma ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok, inda yawon bude ido na Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasa ta halaka dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon buɗe ido a cikin gidaje.
