Sabon bayani game da ruwa mai narkewa: raguwa a Pinellas, Manatees da Sarasotas
Wani sabon rahoto daga Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Rayuwa ta Florida (FWC) ya nuna cewa yawan adadin bitamin da ke ci gaba da ci a yankin Tampa Bay ya ragu.
FWC ta ce an samu rahotanni na samun ci gaba a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier, wanda ke nuna cewa adadin da ake samu a cikinta yana raguwa.
Ana samun ruwa mai zurfi a kusan mil 130 (209 km) daga arewacin Pinellas County zuwa kudancin Lee County.
Ana iya samun 'yan daji a wajen mil 10 daga gabar tekun da ke gundumar Hillsborough, amma adadin wuraren da aka ajiye ya ragu sosai a makon da ya gabata.
Akwai rashin ruwa a gundumar Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata, an samu matsakaitan taro a yankin Pinellas County a bakin teku ko kuma a cikin tekun, ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a yankin Hillsborough County a cikin tekun, ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a yankin Manatee County, ƙananan taro a yankin Sarasota County a bakin teku da kuma a cikin tekun, ƙananan taro a yankin Charlotte County a cikin tekun, ƙananan taro a yankin Lee County a cikin tekun da kuma a cikin tekun, da ƙananan taro a cikin Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahotanni daga Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte, da Collier game da tashin hankali a cikin numfashi.
A cikin makon da ya gabata, ba a samu wani rahoto game da tashin hankali a cikin numfashi a Arewacin Florida ba.
